    "date": "2024-08-13T20:29:15Z",
    "text": "PHE Congressional Review Act\n\nThis bill requires Congress to regularly review whether to continue or end a declared public health emergency.\u00a0\n\nSpecifically, each chamber of Congress must meet within six months of a declaration of a\u00a0national public health emergency, and every six months thereafter until the emergency ends, to consider a vote on a joint resolution as to whether to end\u00a0the emergency."
  },
